name: s63_dumbwaytodie
description: **Dumb Ways to Die** is a hilariously tragic web app that allows users to log in and maintain a personalized list of the weirdest and most bizarre ways people have met their end. Whether it's getting stuck in a vending machine, challenging a goose to a fight, or mistaking a superglue bottle for eye dropsâ€”this app is here to document the most ridiculous send-offs in human history.
